<p>A prototype depicting interactions & flow was created with <a href="https://atomic.io">Atomic</a> to guide and educate visually how a user traverses, and interacts during the quiz experience. Discussions such as how users return to particular points of quiz, selects answers, and accesses each input method within different screen contexts were examined. This helped to maintain a sensible process towards the final results screen. Placement was also discussed to help honor the flow of users traversing through each point of the experience. Since Atomic works quite well with Sketch it allowed for quick syncing between multiple Sketch artboards, and designs allowing new content to be pushed rapidly with ease.</p>

